TestSystemTestGoalNoForeach
/ Structural regression guard: the rewritten system/test.goal uses the three
/ C# test actions (test.discover → test.run → test.report) instead of
/ foreach. Verify those three tokens are present — any regression to the
/ foreach-based runner would drop them.
- read file '/system/test.goal', write to %goalText%
- assert %goalText% contains 'test.discover'
- assert %goalText% contains 'test.run'
- assert %goalText% contains 'test.report'
